  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?\r\n\r\n- [X] Foundry\r\n- [ ] Foundryup\r\n\r\n### What version of Foundry are you on?\r\n\r\nforge 0.2.0 (d3d8c0b 2022-12-24T12:37:56.094597155Z)\r\n\r\n### What command(s) is the bug in?\r\n\r\nforge geiger\r\n\r\n### Operating System\r\n\r\nLinux\r\n\r\n### Describe the bug\r\n\r\n`forge geiger` searches the `lib` folder where it reports false positives. It should ignore the `lib/forge-std` folder. \r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/24715302/209438878-7a2088ab-29f9-49a6-9b74-9598d7bbe11d.png)\r\n",
